        <p class="article-lead">Fact Verification (FV) is a subtask of Fact Extraction and VERification (FEVER) and can be formulated as whether the relationship of given claim and evidence is refute, support, or not enough information <a href="https://aclanthology.org/2021.naacl-main.71/">[Du et al., 2021]</a> <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.05355">[Thorne et al., 2018]</a>.</p>
